# Prompt Optimizer — auction-scraper

Checkpointed pending run artifacts in upwork-agentic-workflow (commit before edits);
claude-workflow-studio was already clean. Applied the safe improvements.md suggestions
as surgical edits to agent prompts + CLAUDE.md. Local commit only, no push.

## Applied (commit 7d77050)
- **researcher.md** — caps: ≤2 fetches per candidate site, no alternate-URL retries;
  403/robots-403 ⇒ assume Playwright-only, stop probing. [pre-researcher tokens+adherence]
- **deploy-test.md** — determine auth by grepping deploy.out/build-report for
  "credentials"/"login" before attempting login; import Playwright by absolute module
  path `.../upwork-agentic-workflow/node_modules/playwright/index.mjs`. [deploy-test reuse+adherence]
- **planner.md** — if it runs before researcher (no research.md), write only a
  <30-line research-questions list and stop; full plan on the post-research pass. [planner tokens]
- **demo-builder.md** — live-streaming demos use POST(job_id)+GET /stream/<id> SSE,
  not a single long streaming GET. [planner adherence]
- **CLAUDE.md** — GitHub handle is `mwegter95` (never `michaelwegter`, 404s); one-time
  Playwright-on-Surface install note (`python -m playwright install chromium`) so
  `playwright_available:false` isn't re-debugged each run. [plan-ceo adherence, demo-builder reuse]

## Not applied (deliberate)
- final-ceo "add em/en-dash auto-scan to proposal-writer" — already present and explicit
